      <title>Pramotedham 谈 2024 财年收益、人工智能炒作和扩张计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-11/pramotedham-on-fy24-earnings-ai-hype-expansion-plans-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿联酋公司 Presight AI 公布了截至 2024 年的全年业绩。该公司的收入创下 22 亿迪拉姆的纪录，比上年增长 24%。Presight AI 首席执行官 Thomas Pramotedham 在彭博电视台的 Horizo​​ns Middle East and Africa 节目中与主持人 Joumanna Bercetche 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-11/pramotedham-on-fy24-earnings-ai-hype-expansion-plans-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 09:23:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>古驰 (Gucci) 股价企稳，推动开云集团业绩增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-11/signs-of-stabilization-at-gucci-boost-kering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[开云集团旗下最大的品牌古驰去年第四季度的营收同比下降了 24%，但成本控制措施帮助开云集团实现了略高于分析师预期的年度利润。彭博社的 Angelina Rascouet 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-11/signs-of-stabilization-at-gucci-boost-kering</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 09:09:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟称将对美国关税采取反制措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/eu-says-it-will-impose-countermeasures-against-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟誓言将对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布的美国将对钢铁和铝进口征收 25% 的关税作出回应，此举将加剧美国与最亲密盟友之一之间的贸易争端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/eu-says-it-will-impose-countermeasures-against-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 08:23:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BP 承诺进行“根本性重置”，激进投资者 Elliott 增持股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/bp-ceo-pledges-strategy-reset-after-intervention-of-activist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国石油公司承诺在即将发布的战略更新中做出重大改变，寻求扭转长期业绩不佳的局面，这一局面目前已吸引了激进投资者埃利奥特投资管理公司 (Elliott Investment Management) 的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/bp-ceo-pledges-strategy-reset-after-intervention-of-activist</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 07:08:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
